name: MetaBET
public_notice: MetaBET (MBET) has recently migrated from their old contract to a new one. For more information, please visit this Twitter post.
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
"Cryptocurrency is rapidly expanding into the Metaverse. We envision our polished platform as the leading Metaverse casino. Picture yourself as a poker player sitting across the table from your favorite celebrity. We intend
to bring life to a professional, trustworthy and user-friendly virtual platform."
